# Guest layer (`src/app/guest`)

Unauthenticated business entry — portal picker, login, company registration. No marketing landing page. Rendered inside shared `AppShellComponent` (see `layout.mdc`).

## Routes (`guest.routes.ts`)

Flat child routes under `AppShellComponent` in `app.routes.ts`:

| Path | Page | Guard |
|------|------|-------|
| `/` | `PortalPickerPageComponent` | `guestGuard` |
| `/login` | `UserLoginPageComponent` | `guestGuard` |
| `/register` | `RegisterCompanyPageComponent` | `guestGuard` |
| `/admin/login` | `AdminLoginPageComponent` | `guestGuard` |

No `/sign-in` route — `SIGN_IN_URL` is `/`.

## Pages (`guest/pages/`)

- `portal-picker/` — portal picker at `/`; includes `PortalCardComponent`
- `user-login/` — user login (shared `login/login.form.ts`, `login-page.component.scss`)
- `admin-login/` — admin login (same shared login assets)
- `login/` — shared `login.form.ts`, `login.model.ts`, `login-page.component.scss` only
- `register/` — company registration stepper (`mode: 'stepper'`): create-only — see `forms.mdc`

## Topbar (guest mode)

Handled by `shared/shell/app-topbar/` — not in guest folder:

- **Always** show Register company (`COMPANY_REGISTER_URL`)
- Show Sign in text link when URL ≠ `/`
- Brand links to `SIGN_IN_URL` (`/`)

## Constants & imports

- App URLs: `shared/constants/guest-urls.ts` (`SIGN_IN_URL`, login/register paths); import via `app-urls.ts` barrel
- Auth: `shared/core/auth/auth.service.ts`
- Guest imports `shared/**` only — do **not** import portal features
